trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Kall `Dispose` når du er ferdig med <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden forlater den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall `Dispose`, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>ble bruker.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall `Dispose` før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Returns all exports that match the conditions of the specified import.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer alle Eksporter som svarer til vilkårene for den angitte importen.

trans-unit.source: Implementers should not treat cardinality-related mismatches as errors and should not throw exceptions for cardinality-related mismatches.
trans-unit.target: Implementerere kan ikke behandle kardinalitet-relaterte typekonflikter under som feil, og bør ikke iverksette unntak for kardinalitet-relaterte typekonflikter under.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the import requests exactly one export and the provider has either no matching exports or more than one, the GetExportsCore method should return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> objects.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis importen ber om nøyaktig én eksport og leverandøren har ingen samsvarende Eksporter eller mer enn én, GetExportsCore-metoden må returnere en tom <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>samling <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>objekter.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>
